extends ../layout

block content
  
  .container-fluid
    .row.row-centered
      .col-md-12.content.corpo
        .col-md-12.company_top(style="background-image: url('/images/nonprofit/header_ageuk_eastlondon.jpg');")
        .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
          .col-md-2.col-sm-3.col-xs-12.profile_photo
            img(src="/images/nonprofit/logo_age_uk_east_london.jpg", alt="logo AgeUK")
          .col-md-10.col-sm-9.col-xs-12
            h3 Age UK East London
          
          .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.not_colored
            h3.text-center.col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-4.col-xs-12 About us
            .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.no-gutter
              p.text-justify
                |Age UK is the country's largest charity dedicated to helping everyone make the most of later life.
                |We believe in a world where everyone can love later life and we work every day to achieve this.
                |With the help of volunteer mentors acting as role models, we aim to bridge the aspirations-attainment gap.
                |By linking young people with inspirational role models in this way, we boost their confidence, self-efficacy and long-term employability.
                br
                br
                | Age UK East London aims to enable older people to:
                br
                ul.disc
                  li
                    | Retain maximum possible choice over the direction of their lives;
                  li
                    | Maintain and improve health;
                  li
                    | Prevent social isolation;
                  li
                    | Live in physical environments suited to their changing needs;
                  li
                    | Have as many opportunities as possible for involvement in fulfilling community and leisure activities.

              .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.break

              .col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.no-gutter
                p 
                  |Website: 
                  a(href="http://www.ageuk.org.uk/eastlondon", rel="external", target="_blank") <em>http://www.ageuk.org.uk/eastlondon</em>
                  br
                  |Phone Number: <em>+44 (0) 208 981 7124</em>
                  br
                  |E-mail: 
                  a(href="mailto:sharon.waddams@ageukeastlondon.org.uk") <em>sharon.waddams@ageukeastlondon.org.uk</em>
              .col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.no-gutter
                p
                  |Location: <br/>
                  em
                    |82 Russia Lane
                    br
                    |London, E2 9LU
          
        .row.row-centered
          .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.colored
            .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
              h3.text-center.col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3.col-xs-12 Volunteer with us
              .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.no-gutter
                p.text-justify
                  |We can only do the things we do with the energy and dedication of our Trustees, staff and volunteers. Age UK East London has a wide range of volunteering opportunities for people with a little spare time to offer.
                  |For full volunteering role description, please visit our  &nbsp;
                  a(href="http://www.ageuk.org.uk/eastlondon/get-involved/volunteering/", target="_blank", rel="external")
                    |website
                  br
                  br
                  |What you can expect from us . . .
                  br
                  br
                  strong
                    |If you become a volunteer with Age UK East London, we:
                  ul.disc
                    li
                      |Provide a role description so you are clear as to what is expected of you
                    li
                      |Offer training and support to enable you to perform your chosen role
                    li
                      |Reimburse certain expenses (e.g. travel)
                  br
                  |What we expect from you . . .
                  br
                  br
                  strong
                    |As one of our volunteers, we expect you to:
                  ul.disc
                    li
                      |Be available regularly (hours per week varies depending on what you volunteer for) with a commitment of at least 6 months
                    li
                      |Ensure you understand and abide by any guidelines associated with your role
                    li
                      |Be reliable, as our clients depend on the services we provide
                    li
                      |Be trustworthy and keep information about clients confidential
                    li
                      |Be a good ambassador for Age UK East London.
            .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.break  

    .row.row-centered
      .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.not_colored
        .col-md-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
          .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.volunteer_list#id_561520c50912c8030015c399
          
          script(src="/javascripts/nonprofitProfilePage.min.js")
            